episodes.title: The Game Show Episode That Exposed a Cult
episodes.description:
A deep-dive into the FLDS cult, Warren Jeffs, and the lost Moment of Truth game show episode that briefly exposed a hidden reality on live television. This documentary explores cult indoctrination, obedience, erased TV footage, and the confession that vanished shortly after it aired.

Thank you so much for watching!

If you have an idea you want me to cover in a video, email me: newfearfiles@gmail.com
